   "source": [
    "## Resolution\n",
    "\n",
    "In normal, CoolBox will select proper resolution automatically from your\n",
    "multi-resolution `.hic` or `.mcool` file, but you can also specify it\n",
    "by your self."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "test_hic = \"../../../tests/test_data/dothic_chr9_4000000_6000000.hic\""
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "10Kb resolution:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1133.86x362.835 with 7 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 4,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "dhic = DotHiC(test_hic, cmap=\"RdYlBu_r\", depth_ratio=.5, resolution=10000)\n",
    "frame = XAxis() + dhic\n",
    "frame.plot(\"chr9:4000000-6000000\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "25Kb resolution:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1133.86x362.835 with 7 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 5,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "dhic = DotHiC(test_hic, cmap=\"RdYlBu_r\", depth_ratio=.5, resolution=25000)\n",
    "frame = XAxis() + dhic\n",
    "frame.plot(\"chr9:4000000-6000000\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Balance\n",
    "\n",
    "You can use `balance` to control do matrix balance or not.\n",
    "The default behavior do balance, we can turn off it:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1133.86x362.835 with 7 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 6,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "dhic = DotHiC(test_hic, balance=False, cmap=\"RdYlBu_r\", depth_ratio=.5, resolution=10000)\n",
    "frame = XAxis() + dhic\n",
    "frame.plot(\"chr9:4000000-6000000\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "In addition, `.hic` file support three kinds of matrix balance method:\n",
    "* VC\n",
    "* VC_SQRT\n",
    "* KR (default)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1133.86x816.945 with 15 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 7,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "with Feature(resolution=10000), Feature(depth_ratio=0.4), Color(\"RdYlBu_r\"):\n",
    "    dhic_vc = DotHiC(test_hic, balance=\"VC\")\n",
    "    dhic_vcs = DotHiC(test_hic, balance=\"VC_SQRT\")\n",
    "    dhic_kr = DotHiC(test_hic, balance=\"KR\")\n",
    "\n",
    "frame = XAxis() + \\\n",
    "    dhic_vc + Title(\"VC\") + \\\n",
    "    dhic_vcs + Title(\"VC_SQRT\") + \\\n",
    "    dhic_kr + Title(\"KR\")\n",
    "frame.plot(\"chr9:4000000-6000000\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Normalize\n",
    "\n",
    "CoolBox can perform three kinds of normazation on the matrix(balanced or non-balanced):\n",
    "\n",
    "- total: Divide the total value of the local region.\n",
    "- expect: Divide the mean value alone the specifed distance dialog.\n",
    "- zscore: (matrix - mean) / std"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {
    "scrolled": false,
    "tags": [
     "nbsphinx-thumbnail"
    ]
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1133.86x1071.78 with 22 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 8,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "with Feature(resolution=10000, depth_ratio=0.4, color=\"RdYlBu_r\"):\n",
    "    dhic_b = DotHiC(test_hic, balance=\"KR\")\n",
    "    dhic_ub = DotHiC(test_hic, balance=False)\n",
    "    with Feature(transform=False, norm=False, gaussian_sigma=0.7, max_value=5, min_value=-2):\n",
    "        dhic_exp = DotHiC(test_hic, normalize='expect')\n",
    "        dhic_z = DotHiC(test_hic, normalize='zscore')\n",
    "\n",
    "frame = XAxis() + \\\n",
    "    dhic_ub + Title(\"Original\\n(Unbalanced)\") + \\\n",
    "    dhic_b + Title(\"balanced\") + \\\n",
    "    dhic_exp + Title(\"Expect\") + \\\n",
    "    HLine() + \\\n",
    "    dhic_z + Title(\"Z-score\")\n",
    "frame.plot(\"chr9:4000000-6000000\")"
   ]
  }
